@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Created
Created --> Reviewed : submit
Reviewed --> Pending : review
Pending --> Archived : approve
Pending : entry / log transaction
Archived --> Created : revert
Archived --> [*]
@enduml